description: Chef Dan's Southern Comfort travels around Indianapolis and central Indiana to community events and festivals sharing our great food featuring Chef Dan's Mississippi Rub.  If you need a unique food vendor for your festival, contact us today.Full flavors from the Mississippi Delta and Louisiana Bayou. Menu items include rib tips, cajun prime rib sandwiches, mac n cheese, cajun potato salad, and more.  We also offer a  New Orleans food booth, items such as Chicken & Sausage Jambalaya or Red Beans and Rice with fresh Beignets!
name: Chef Dan's Southern Comfort
